---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Buy a Home"
  description="Buy your dream home in San Diego with Rusty Rau. Expert guidance for first-time buyers, investors, and families navigating the competitive San Diego market."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="page-hero buyers-hero">
    <div class="hero-background">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600596542815-ffad4c1539a9?w=1920&q=80" alt="Beautiful San Diego home" class="hero-image" loading="eager">
      <div class="hero-overlay dark"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <span class="hero-tag">For Buyers</span>
      <h1 class="hero-title">Find Your<br><span class="accent">Dream Home</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Navigate the competitive San Diego market with an expert by your side. From first showing to keys in hand, I've got you covered.</p>
      <div class="hero-cta-group">
        <a href="/contact" class="cta-button">Start Your Search</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro Section -->
  <section class="content-section alt-bg">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="intro-content">
        <h2 class="section-title">Buying in San Diego Doesn't Have to Be Overwhelming</h2>
        <p class="lead-text">
          The San Diego real estate market moves fast. Between competitive offers, tight inventory, and high stakes, having the right agent isn't just helpful—it's essential.
        </p>
        <p>
          I've helped dozens of buyers—from first-timers to seasoned investors—find and win the perfect home. My approach combines deep local knowledge, strategic thinking, and genuine care for your success. When you work with me, you get more than an agent. You get a trusted advisor who's as invested in finding your home as you are.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Me Section -->
  <section class="content-section alt-bg">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-tag center">The Difference</span>
      <h2 class="section-title center">Why Buyers Choose Rusty</h2>
      
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-map-marked-alt"></i></div>
          <h3>Local Knowledge</h3>
          <p>Born and raised in San Diego, I know every neighborhood—the hidden gems, the up-and-coming areas, and the communities that match your lifestyle.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-trophy"></i></div>
          <h3>Winning Strategies</h3>
          <p>In a competitive market, the right offer strategy can make or break your chances. I'll help you craft offers that stand out and give you the best shot at winning.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-user-shield"></i></div>
          <h3>Your Advocate</h3>
          <p>I work for you, not the seller. From negotiations to inspections, I protect your interests and ensure you're making a sound investment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-clock"></i></div>
          <h3>Patient & Responsive</h3>
          <p>Whether you're ready to move fast or need time to explore, I match your pace. And when a great property hits the market, I'll make sure you're first to know.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i></div>
          <h3>Education First</h3>
          <p>Buying a home is a big decision. I'll walk you through every step, explain your options, and make sure you understand the process.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-network-wired"></i></div>
          <h3>Connected Resources</h3>
          <p>Need a lender, inspector, or contractor? I've built relationships with trusted professionals who will take care of you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who I Help Section -->
  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-tag center">Who I Help</span>
      <h2 class="section-title center">Specialized Experience</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Whether you're buying your first home or your fifth, I have the experience to help you succeed.</p>
      
      <div class="specialties-grid">
        <div class="specialty-card">
          <div class="specialty-icon"><i class="fas fa-key"></i></div>
          <h3>First-Time Homebuyers</h3>
          <p>The process can feel overwhelming, but it doesn't have to be. I'll guide you through every step, from getting pre-approved to negotiating your offer.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="specialty-card">
          <div class="specialty-icon"><i class="fas fa-medal"></i></div>
          <h3>Military & Veterans</h3>
          <p>I understand VA loans and the unique needs of our military community. Whether you're PCSing to San Diego or separating and putting down roots, I'll help.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="specialty-card">
          <div class="specialty-icon"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i></div>
          <h3>Investors</h3>
          <p>Looking for rental properties or fix-and-flips? I'll help you analyze deals, understand market dynamics, and find properties with strong investment potential.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="specialty-card">
          <div class="specialty-icon"><i class="fas fa-gem"></i></div>
          <h3>Luxury Buyers</h3>
          <p>San Diego's luxury market requires discretion, market knowledge, and access. I represent buyers seeking exceptional properties in La Jolla, Del Mar, and beyond.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="specialty-card">
          <div class="specialty-icon"><i class="fas fa-plane-arrival"></i></div>
          <h3>Relocating Families</h3>
          <p>Moving to San Diego? I'll be your boots on the ground—touring homes on video calls, providing neighborhood insights, and coordinating everything.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="specialty-card">
          <div class="specialty-icon"><i class="fas fa-exchange-alt"></i></div>
          <h3>Move-Up Buyers</h3>
          <p>Ready for more space? I'll help you navigate the timing of selling and buying, find your next dream home, and make the transition smooth.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process Section -->
  <section class="content-section alt-bg process-section">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-tag center">The Process</span>
      <h2 class="section-title center">Your Path to Homeownership</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">A clear roadmap from search to keys</p>
      
      <div class="process-timeline">
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">01</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Initial Consultation</h3>
            <ul class="step-list">
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Discuss your goals, needs, and timeline</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Understand your must-haves and nice-to-haves</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Review the buying process together</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Identify neighborhoods that match your lifestyle</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">02</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Financial Preparation</h3>
            <ul class="step-list">
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Connect you with trusted lenders</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Get pre-approved for a mortgage</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Understand your buying power</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Review loan options (conventional, VA, FHA)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">03</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>The Home Search</h3>
            <ul class="step-list">
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Set up custom property alerts</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Access to listings before they hit the market</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Tour homes at your pace</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Find the right home—not just any home</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">04</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Making Your Offer</h3>
            <ul class="step-list">
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Analyze comparable sales</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Craft a competitive offer strategy</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Write a strong, compelling offer</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Negotiate price and terms</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">05</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Due Diligence</h3>
            <ul class="step-list">
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Coordinate home inspection</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Review inspection reports together</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Negotiate repairs or credits if needed</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Finalize your mortgage</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">06</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Closing & Keys</h3>
            <ul class="step-list">
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Final walk-through of the property</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Sign closing documents</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Get your keys and celebrate!</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Welcome home</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonial Highlight -->
  <section class="testimonial-highlight">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="highlight-card">
        <div class="quote-icon"><i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i></div>
        <p class="highlight-text">"We were first time home buyers trying to buy in a very competitive market, and Rusty helped us navigate the process with patience and honesty. We always felt like he had our best interests at heart."</p>
        <div class="highlight-author">
          <span class="author-name">Daniel B.</span>
          <span class="author-detail">Bought a home in Normal Heights</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Areas Section -->
  <section class="content-section alt-bg">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-tag center">Explore San Diego</span>
      <h2 class="section-title center">Neighborhoods I Know Best</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">From beach towns to family-friendly suburbs, I'll help you find the community that fits your life.</p>
      
      <div class="areas-showcase">
        <div class="area-box">
          <div class="area-box-icon"><i class="fas fa-umbrella-beach"></i></div>
          <h3>Coastal Communities</h3>
          <p>La Jolla, Del Mar, Encinitas, Solana Beach, Carlsbad, Pacific Beach</p>
        </div>
        <div class="area-box">
          <div class="area-box-icon"><i class="fas fa-users"></i></div>
          <h3>Family Neighborhoods</h3>
          <p>Carmel Valley, Scripps Ranch, Poway, Rancho Bernardo, 4S Ranch</p>
        </div>
        <div class="area-box">
          <div class="area-box-icon"><i class="fas fa-city"></i></div>
          <h3>Urban Living</h3>
          <p>Downtown, Hillcrest, North Park, Mission Hills, Little Italy</p>
        </div>
        <div class="area-box">
          <div class="area-box-icon"><i class="fas fa-gem"></i></div>
          <h3>Luxury Estates</h3>
          <p>Rancho Santa Fe, Del Mar, La Jolla Farms, Coronado, Point Loma</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="center-cta">
        <a href="/neighborhoods" class="cta-button secondary">Explore All Neighborhoods</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <h2>Ready to Start Your Home Search?</h2>
      <p>Let's talk about your goals and find your perfect San Diego home together.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="cta-button">Schedule a Consultation</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
